{"id": 2922, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，什么事情会让你觉得生活重新开始了？", "description": "关于你的“一键刷新”时刻，欢迎来分享。（题图来自：istock ©️ bortonia）", "record_count": 3142, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190506130351f8VLyInm26zNJpWt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-03T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 342528, "content": "撕了这一页纸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648570}, {"id": 342529, "content": "回家后返回工作的城市", "image": "img/option/option/20190504224241ihMF1DObSqr25xsa", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648530}, {"id": 342785, "content": "睡醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1633295}, {"id": 342531, "content": "还马云爸爸的花呗和信用卡算吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826091}, {"id": 342277, "content": "删光了所有朋友圈/说说", "image": "img/option/option/20190504011154WLrHfeAQk4m3ciuJ", "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519126}, {"id": 342533, "content": "停下脚步，修正一段时间，换个地点换种心情，重新出发", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576785}, {"id": 342278, "content": "离开高中 来到大学。", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519126}, {"id": 342534, "content": "跑完步 大汗淋漓 洗完澡后", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648103}, {"id": 342790, "content": "养了一些动植物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254552}, {"id": 342279, "content": "重新开始一份工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 343, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 342535, "content": "每月一痛 走了之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681724}, {"id": 342280, "content": "一觉醒来", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574846}, {"id": 342536, "content": "早上睁开眼睛都时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1639092}, {"id": 342281, "content": "洗澡洗头洗脸都洗了一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 688, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1193901}, {"id": 342537, "content": "被动或主动的离开最依赖的人之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648581}, {"id": 342282, "content": "结束思考自杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340666}, {"id": 342538, "content": "结了个婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459576}, {"id": 342283, "content": "在宿舍厕所里悄悄抽完一根烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505253}, {"id": 342539, "content": "搬家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481119}, {"id": 342284, "content": "犹豫了一晚上想跳楼，上了楼顶天见亮，在楼顶看完朝阳，下楼吃了一碗馄炖，回家深思熟虑定了张计划表，第三天开始当活人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378318}, {"id": 342540, "content": "每一天起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1636316}, {"id": 342285, "content": "生活就像一本历史书那么沉重，对我来说，无法重新开始啊🤕🤕", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386990}, {"id": 342541, "content": "去一个没有人认识的地方\n有一个新的起点\n\n和过去无关的起点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648592}, {"id": 342286, "content": "近距离揭开美的面纱，然后回家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549196}, {"id": 342542, "content": "困到翻白眼睡完觉之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576910}, {"id": 342287, "content": "她给我说了晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556311}, {"id": 342799, "content": "完成周计划时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631697}, {"id": 342288, "content": "大病初愈", "image": null, "praise_count": 159, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647857}, {"id": 342544, "content": "她走后的对生活的陌生，很幸运遇见她。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592039}, {"id": 342289, "content": "自慰", "image": null, "praise_count": 212, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1411613}, {"id": 342545, "content": "回了一趟家，然后又坐上离家的火车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1365918}, {"id": 342546, "content": "老公出轨后，我吃安眠药自杀，未遂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547590}, {"id": 342291, "content": "最爱的人还有几天就回上海了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195977}, {"id": 342547, "content": "跟妈妈诉说大哭一场", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648612}, {"id": 342292, "content": "失恋分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 415346}, {"id": 342548, "content": "找一个我爱的男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640159}, {"id": 342294, "content": "早晨起床洗澡去上课", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339105}, {"id": 342550, "content": "认真的学习状态后", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710726}, {"id": 342295, "content": "前几周崩溃到极致，痛哭一整晚，根本睡不着也没有心情睡。我的猫就在旁边安安静静陪着我，到了早上，外面的鸟叫吵到了猫，她奔去阳台并为我拉开了窗帘。阳光洒在我身上，那一刻我决定重启自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647860}, {"id": 342551, "content": "假期结束，马上又要投入新的学习生活了，一切都值得期待呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648636}, {"id": 342296, "content": "上B站  鬼畜  学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1435439}, {"id": 343833, "content": "把TODO列表清空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602542}, {"id": 342298, "content": "赶完deadline/结束期末考", "image": null, "praise_count": 268, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557630}, {"id": 342554, "content": "新的想法付诸实践", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939021}, {"id": 342299, "content": "悠哉悠哉休息了一天 又重新获得了好好生活的动力", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511663}, {"id": 342300, "content": "买车", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1629224}, {"id": 342557, "content": "旅行后\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1292442}, {"id": 342302, "content": "一会到家啥也不想蒙头大睡到第二天", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1346544}, {"id": 342558, "content": "扔东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363640}, {"id": 342303, "content": "工资大幅度增长", "image": null, "praise_count": 76, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}]}